            <title>[LU-2459] ZFS OSD does not check LMA incompat flag </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2459</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ZFS OSD should check that the LMA incompatibility flags and return an error if some incompat flag aren&apos;t supported. See osd_get_lma() in OSD ldiskfs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
